{"data":[{"date":"21:32 01/08","title":"Mourinho ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng Martial v\u00ec th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng Martial 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec b\u1ecf t\u1eadp \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Carrington chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ng\u00e0y khai m\u00e0n Premier League.</h2><h2>Martial v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho cho ph\u00e9p r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Man United t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee9a con m\u1edbi ra \u0111\u1eddi. C\u1eadu con trai th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Martial mang t\u00ean Swan \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 6 ng\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Martial s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Carrington tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i bay v\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Real. Nh\u01b0ng Martial c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea1t Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng Martial v\u00ec th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng Martial v\u00ec th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng Martial v\u00ec th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd The Sun, Martial s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 180.000 b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u1edbi Martial v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u1ed7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real Madrid, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y Martial khi m\u1edf l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPh\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mang t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng t\u1eeb tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u00e2y gi\u1edd Martial \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n khi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Manchester sau \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Martial \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford. V\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1edd m\u1ecbt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Martial:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\">Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U, th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Martial \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho-172-192306.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u201cdanh s\u00e1ch \u0111en\u201d c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1890","checkdouble":"192498"},{"date":"21:40 01/08","title":"Arsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/4EC04E8E00000578-6016759-image-m-71_1533159211254.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u00cdt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 song Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau khi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f2n Cech ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Loftus-Cheek n\u00ean th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Emery.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: ARSENAL 1-1 (PEN 6-5) CHELSEA\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf HLV t\u1ea1i Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 th\u00e1ng.  Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi\u1ebfn  Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c. \u00d4ng gi\u00fap Arsenal ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c v\u1ecb  tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhau r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, bi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1eafn  r\u1ecfi, gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u  t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u1edf h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngay t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i  nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1 n\u1ebfp sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u0169. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Wenger th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf trong v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f3ng  k\u00edn c\u1eeda, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi trao c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd. Trong khi  \u0111\u00f3, HLV Emery t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ecdi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00d4ng \u0103n c\u00f9ng, t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi giao ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra  s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t  bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 gia t\u0103ng t\u00ednh k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u  th\u1ee7 Arsenal khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1edd \u0103n tr\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i hay c\u00e1c  thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed kh\u00e1c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0103n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i 1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EC04E8E00000578-6016759-image-m-71_1533159211254.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTh\u1ebf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n bao tr\u00f9m Arsenal. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ef1 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n, g\u1ea7n  g\u0169i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra cho h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao  h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Emile  Smith-Rowe \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean  \u0111\u1ea5t Singapore. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi  Chelsea, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u PSG v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. V\u00ec  th\u1ebf m\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n nay HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba  qua, c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alexandre Lacazette v\u00e0 Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t sung  m\u00e3n, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt  tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ea1i Nga. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c  m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Eden Hazard, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a  Chelsea tr\u1edf n\u00ean thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn  Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh London phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ICC 2018 n\u00e0y, HLV Emery kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 c\u1eb7p  Lacazette vs Aubameyang tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1eafm m\u1ed7i Aubameyang n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u.  H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon l\u00e0 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00f9a  tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Ozil c\u00f9ng Mkhitaryan. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 do t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb kh\u00e1  n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua Emile Smith-Rowe (thay Ramsey d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n  th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng), Elneny c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n binh Matteo Guendouzi. T\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng  ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c: trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis  Papastathopoulos.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea\" title=\"Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EBFF60200000578-0-image-a-11_1533152160836.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rudiger m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>B\u00ean ph\u00eda Chelsea, HLV Sarri - m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i CLB n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Premier  League n\u00f3i chung gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn - v\u1eabn gi\u1eef quan \u0111i\u1ec3m  \"1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng n\u00ean c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u  nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 Chelsea b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch cho c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. \u1ea4y th\u1ebf m\u00e0  so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Inter Milan tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i h\u00f4m c\u0169ng t\u1ea1i  ICC 2018, danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a The Blues ch\u1ec9 thay \u0111\u00fang 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m \u1edf h\u1ec7  th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1: Caballero thay \u0111\u00e0n em Bucka \u1edf khung g\u1ed7, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c  Rudiger th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Ampadu v\u00e0 Azpilicueta tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i thay  Zappacosta.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0  g\u1eafn k\u1ebft cao cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat  th\u1ee9 5. Sau khi Petr Cech - th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh danh \u1edf The Blues - t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u00fa ra  ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Fabregas, Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh F4 \u0111\u00e3 treo b\u00f3ng  cho trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi CLB l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m Chelsea ch\u01a1i h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n v\u00e0 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Arsenal. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 14,  \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho r\u1eb1ng Bellerin ph\u1ea1m  l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Hudson-Odoi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 2000. Song \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc thay, Morata l\u1ea1i  kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Petr Cech tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Ph\u00fat 24, v\u1eabn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  \u0111\u00e0n em Hudson-Odoi trao m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c  n\u1ed5i Cech trong pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1, Arsenal ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n  Chelsea. Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 32, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong  tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ozil \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng cho Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Armenia c\u0103ng ngang nguy  hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0ng Aubameyang \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ee5t khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n ch\u01b0a  \u0111\u1ea7y 5m.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EC0406F00000578-6016759-image-a-43_1533157720105.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lacazette g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Arsenal v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, Arsenal ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng ph\u00fat  41, ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cech khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Hudson-Odoi trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng  \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Emery m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9  gi\u1ea3i lao, Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp  c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m tung  m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p>Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m nguy. Ph\u00fat  57, v\u1eabn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t  d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c. C\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 theo  \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi Sarri th\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t  kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Emery th\u00ec h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 75, Lacazette m\u1edbi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 ngo\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Christensen  trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Chelsea r\u1ed3i s\u00fat ch\u00ecm v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i.  Ph\u00fat 84, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t l\u00e0m ng\u01a1 v\u1edbi Arsenal khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bulka  \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Iwobi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EBFEC3B00000578-6016759-image-a-15_1533153515715.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cech \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, d\u00e0n  \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i c\u00f2i  k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Arsenal m\u1edbi g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. Ozil c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \"l\u01b0\u1eddm rau g\u1eafp  th\u1ecbt\" qu\u00e1 hay cho Nelson v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i 18 \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng ngang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa v\u00f2ng  c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Lacazette \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>V\u1eady l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf ICC 2018, Chelsea l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m  lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Inter Milan \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang (c\u0169ng h\u00f2a 1-1  sau 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c). 5 lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat d\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai  \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m (Drinkwater, Abraham, Moses, Emerson, Lucas Piazon b\u00ean ph\u00eda  Chelsea v\u00e0 Lacazette, Nelson, Guendouzi, Maitland-Niles, Ozil b\u00ean ph\u00eda Arsenal)  song \u1edf lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat th\u1ee9 6 th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Petr Cech l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 trong tr\u1eadn  \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng 11m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Loftus-Cheek trong  khi Iwobi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho  Arsenal.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nARSENAL (4-3-3):</strong> Petr Cech; Hector Bellerin (Chambers 80'), Shkodran Mustafi, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Sead Kolasinac (Maitland-Niles 70'); Emile Smith-Rowe (Iwobi 63'), Mohamed Elneny, Matteo Guendouzi; Henrikh Mkhitaryan (Nelson 71'), Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang (Lacazette 71'), Mezut Ozil.<br>\r\n<strong>CHELSEA (4-3-3):</strong> Willy Caballero (Bulka 78'); Cezar Azpilicueta (Zappacosta 63'), Antonio Rudiger (Ampadu 63'), David Luiz (Christensen 46'), Marcos Alonso (Emerson 63'); Jorginho (Loftus-Cheek 78'); Ross Barkley (Bakayoko 78'), Cesc Fabregas (Drinkwater 46'); Pedro (Moses 63'), Alvaro Morata (Abraham 63'), Callum Hudson-Odoi (Piazon 86').</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1889","checkdouble":"192499"},{"date":"22:29 01/08","title":"Pires d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/pires-du-doan-lacazette-se-toa-sang-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean Everton tr\u00e1nh xa trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng h\u1edb gi\u00e1 cao.</h2><h2>Everton ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Rojo\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 Everton mua Rojo Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 Everton mua Rojo Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rojo thay Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 Rojo n\u1ed5i l\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV Marco Silva \u01b0u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Man United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng Man United v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tham gia v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y sau khi b\u1ecb Barca kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Yerry Mina. The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Catalonia v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rojo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u00ean gia Ross Dyer c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0i ESPN kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec v\u1edbi tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMarcos Rojo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Everton l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec Man United c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Rojo t\u1edbi Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u01b0? T\u00f4i s\u1ebd khuy\u00ean h\u1ecd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng. Tr\u00e1nh th\u1eadt xa th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ra\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi anh. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Everton\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nRojo \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 107 l\u1ea7n cho Man United tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Sporting Lisbon n\u0103m 2014. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Rojo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-chap-nhan-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-neu-172-192428.html\">Everton ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-172-192398.html\">Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1888","checkdouble":"192500"},{"date":"22:16 01/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng tin kh\u00f4ng vui\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u ba tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 15, 17, 21/8 nh\u01b0 l\u1ecbch c\u0169, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u2018li\u1ec1n t\u00f9 t\u00ec\u2019 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 14, 16 v\u00e0 19/8. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a qu\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat b\u1edbt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Pakistan ng\u00e0y 14/8, g\u1eb7p Nepal ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u2018th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng\u2019 g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thay v\u00ec 4 ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, tr\u00e1nh r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Cikarang, qu\u1eadn Bekasi, mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y Java, Indonesia). Trong khi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Patriot (c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c Bekasi). C\u0169ng theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, hai tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1 l\u00fac 16h00, c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal \u0111\u00e1 l\u00fac 19h00.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c n\u1eefa \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n 8 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf hai b\u1ea3ng D, F thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu) tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00ean l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp, l\u00e0m quen s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm s\u00e2n ph\u1ee5 t\u1eadp c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 8 \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch c\u0169, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 11/8. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm h\u01a1n 1 ng\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh s\u1edbm 1 ng\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 g\u1eb7p Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1887","checkdouble":"192501"},{"date":"22:31 01/08","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/trung-ve-bui-tien-dung-he-lo-ve-phuong-phap-ren-quan-loi-hai-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 m\u00e0 anh kh\u00e1 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eafc t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PVF. Nh\u00ecn chung t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/854_dmhl1694-15331285268411369056055.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u2018n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng\u2019 v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p khi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 m\u00e0 anh kh\u00e1 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eafc t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB Viettel n\u00f3i: \"Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u1ea7y Park \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Th\u1ea7y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ec1 ra. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kho\u1ea3ng hai ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp trung, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea7n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, t\u1ea1o ra c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, c\u00f2n khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n th\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 tin\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Palestine tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 Asiad. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Palestine s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 3/8 t\u1edbi. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1886","checkdouble":"192502"},{"date":"23:17 01/08","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean Everton tr\u00e1nh xa trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng h\u1edb gi\u00e1 cao.</h2><h2>Everton ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Rojo\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 Everton mua Rojo Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 Everton mua Rojo Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rojo thay Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 Rojo n\u1ed5i l\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV Marco Silva \u01b0u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Man United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng Man United v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tham gia v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y sau khi b\u1ecb Barca kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Yerry Mina. The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Catalonia v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rojo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u00ean gia Ross Dyer c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0i ESPN kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec v\u1edbi tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMarcos Rojo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Everton l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec Man United c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Rojo t\u1edbi Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u01b0? T\u00f4i s\u1ebd khuy\u00ean h\u1ecd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng. Tr\u00e1nh th\u1eadt xa th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ra\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi anh. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Everton\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nRojo \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 107 l\u1ea7n cho Man United tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Sporting Lisbon n\u0103m 2014. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Rojo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-chap-nhan-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-neu-172-192428.html\">Everton ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-172-192398.html\">Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1885","checkdouble":"192503"},{"date":"23:25 01/08","title":"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t, vi\u1ec7c VTV th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3i khen.</h2><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM d\u00e0nh cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang gia t\u0103ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng &lsquo;h\u00e9t gi\u00e1&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e9p VTV ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n World Cup v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin VTV kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AISAD 2018 v\u00ec chi ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 cao. Vi\u1ec7c b\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/ve-xem-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-re-bat-ngo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ASIAD, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft VTV c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i AFF Cup 2018, v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la. T\u1ef1u chung nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh BLV Quang Huy c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao cho \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu. Do \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1, gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t hot. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd tr\u1edf \u0111i, ta c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nhanh l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u00e9p gi\u00e1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y VTV \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p, d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>V\u1eabn c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem ASIAD?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ASIAD 2018 tung ra, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi 99% VTV s\u1ebd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n k\u1ef3 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 18 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 VTV ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &quot;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0ng&quot; v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.&nbsp;Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1edb, VTV t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u00ec chi ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 cao, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady t\u1edbi ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a hai t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Viettel v\u00e0 Vingroup, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VTV\" title=\"VTV\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/anh_wc2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VTV kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecf ra h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV c\u0169ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu b\u00ean b\u00e1n l\u00e0 KJSMWORLD CORP ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VTV chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a VTV l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, VTV v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hay kh\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VTV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1eebng l\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u00ean b\u00e1n ch\u1ecbu gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1, ho\u1eb7c VTV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 'm\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n' \u0111\u1ee9ng sau t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, chuy\u1ec7n mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd &lsquo;ngh\u1ec9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rsquo; m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao - v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean&rsquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng, sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\">Sau ASIAD, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup</span><br>\r\nSau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup v\u00ec m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\">VTV tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 do ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t cao khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1884","checkdouble":"192504"},{"date":"06:02 02/08","title":"\u0110\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra tung t\u00edch c\u1ee7a sao M.U bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/sao-mu-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-mat-tich-nhung-ngay-qua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Martial bi\u1ec7t t\u00edch v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Anthony Martial xin ph\u00e9p tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu con trai. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ph\u00e9p, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Man United khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Martial quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi M.U h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi kh\u00f4ng quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang h\u1eb9n. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/sao-mu-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-mat-tich-nhung-ngay-qua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Martial h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Anthony Martial c\u00f3 em b\u00e9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb sau khi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh kh\u1ecfe, xinh \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y ngay nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi h\u00f4m qua, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup, Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 c\u00f2n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn \u0111ang x\u00f4n xao, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, con g\u00e1i m\u1edbi xinh c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng sau khi sinh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 trong tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial\" title=\"Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. &ldquo;C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Swan b\u00e9 nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb9, lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ed5 t\u00e2m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u01a1n Ch\u00faa c\u00f4 \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n&rdquo;, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Twitter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Xin l\u1ed7i nh\u01b0ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u&hellip; Ng\u00e0y mai, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial t\u1ea1i M.U v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho&hellip; Martial</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tien-dao-martial-khoe-anh-con-trai-moi-chao-doi-188-192135.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Martial khoe \u1ea3nh con trai m\u1edbi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-perisic-thay-martial-172-192116.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/martial-bo-do-du-dau-cua-mu-de-cham-vo-sinh-con-188-192079.html\">Martial b\u1ecf d\u1edf du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m v\u1ee3 sinh con</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1883","checkdouble":"192506"},{"date":"06:22 02/08","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Darmian</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Ashley Young ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p h\u1eadu World Cup 2018, Antonio Valencia l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang ra M.U \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1ef1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Diego Dalot t\u1eeb Porto. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i \u0111ang ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n Valencia. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 15/9 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Darmian-cua-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian song b\u1ecb M.U ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, M.U quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Matteo Darmian. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eebng ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n M.U c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Napoli g\u1eedi t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli ch\u01b0a b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Napoli \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3n Darmian trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a. Sau khi b\u1ecb kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 xem x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t sau \u0111\u00f3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di-172-192213.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di-172-192213.html\">M\u1eb7c Mourinho c\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7n, \u201c\u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i</span><br>\r\n<span>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Matteo Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb M.U nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb c\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t, Napoli s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang Serge Aurier c\u1ee7a Tottenham. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Kieran Trippier. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Trippier c\u00f3 v\u1ebb l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01a1n t\u1eeb HLV Mauricio Pochettino. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u Napoli mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Aurier s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, Spurs t\u1eebng m\u1ea5t 23 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang anh v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-bi-mat-dam-phan-chieu-mo-pogba-180-192489.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/btc-icc-to-ra-thong-cam-voi-mourinho-ve-luc-luong-172-192359.html\">BTC ICC t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong-172-192337.html\">M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Khi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-harry-maguire-172-192285.html\">MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muon-co-lewandowski-mu-phai-lam-duoc-dieu-nay-172-192284.html\">Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1882","checkdouble":"192507"},{"date":"06:46 02/08","title":"\u201cTr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o\u201d x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Milan ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/8/trong-phao-xac-nhan-sap-den-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Rossoneri ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Milan</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Gonzalo Higuain. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecf ra 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina m\u00f9a n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro 1 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ph\u00eda c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Higuain. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2018 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 9,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a d\u00f9 Milan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 7,5 tri\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m qua khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, HLV Gennaro Gattuso kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Higuain hay ch\u01b0a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/Ket-qua-C1---Thong-ke-tran-dau-Tottenham-1-2-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc nh\u1ecf. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan sau khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi 3 b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung, Higuain \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Sky Sport r\u1eb1ng: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n, ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 5 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Argentina n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c C\u0110V AC Milan v\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Higuain t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 55 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 105 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh c\u00f9ng Bianconeri \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n gi\u00e0nh 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 Coppa Italia c\u00f9ng 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17 nh\u01b0ng thua Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chiellini-noi-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-192376.html\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sep-lon-napoli-chi-trich-ronaldo-la-hop-dong-thuong-mai-176-192360.html\">S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/roi-juventus-buffon-mien-luon-binh-luan-ve-ronaldo-176-192279.html\">R\u1eddi Juventus, Buffon mi\u1ec5n lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1881","checkdouble":"192508"},{"date":"14:49 01/08","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/chelsea-san-sang-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-gonzalo-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn Higuain kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i, anh kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. AC Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Vuot-mat-AC-Milan,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a tin AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Gonzalo Higuain. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 16 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a sau \u0111\u00f3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 ng\u00e0y, t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp 3 b\u00ean gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Higuain, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Leonardo c\u1ee7a AC Milan v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n Higuain \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-len-tieng-vu-ban-higuain-cho-ac-milan-176-192462.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span>. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft c\u1ea3, Higuain v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan v\u1ee5 Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 AC Milan v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Higuain, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Khi m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng qua th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/chelsea-san-sang-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-gonzalo-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan v\u1ee5 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, Chelsea t\u00ednh ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb Higuain, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Chelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn 2 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb AC Milan.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Stamford Bridge, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, Morata ho\u1eb7c Giroud s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1880","checkdouble":"192472"},{"date":"14:46 01/08","title":"Sao M.U: \"HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/sao-mu-hlv-mourinho-dang-rat-hanh-phuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHerrera cho bi\u1ebft Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tour du \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Man United, khi h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Ed Woodward c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t t\u00e2n binh Fred l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00e1nh n\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n che tan m\u00e2y m\u00f9 c\u1ee7a M.U, ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. HLV Mourinho t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c khi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 cho M.U &ndash; Herrera cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. HLV \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u00f4ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu. Jose h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho\" title=\"Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/sao-mu-hlv-mourinho-dang-rat-hanh-phuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu HLV mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c cho Man United trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi CLB v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i cho 1 trong 5 CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft &ndash; 9 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\">Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U, th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Martial \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin vui bu\u1ed3n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1879","checkdouble":"192473"},{"date":"16:00 01/08","title":"Valverde \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, PSG chi 222 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar t\u1eeb Barca. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Javier-Pastore-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-neymar-gia-350-trieu-euro-180-188122.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 290 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Neymar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar PSG\" title=\"Neymar PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/dong-doi-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o Neymar r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh\u00a0ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh sau khi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Neymar s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar ghi 19 b\u00e0n sau 20 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Song v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Brazil b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1878","checkdouble":"192474"},{"date":"16:26 01/08","title":"Thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, HLV Tottenham chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u00e0i \u201ch\u00e0ng nh\u00e0\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-pochettino-hua-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Tottenham t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t do m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Mauricio Pochettino v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 trong s\u1ed1 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. H\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Roma 4-1, th\u1eafng Milan 1-0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua Barca tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m sau khi h\u00f2a 2-2 \u1edf th\u1eddi gian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham trong m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/HLV-Pochettino-hua-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-Tottenham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00f3i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan. \u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Roma, Barcelona v\u00e0 Milan. Th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i 1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV \u1edf h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham vs Milan\" title=\"Tottenham vs Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/hlv-pochettino-hua-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Amos l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \"m\u1ea7m non\" Spurs t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPochettino n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cSau 4 n\u0103m, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i lo s\u1ee3 khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb? H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Harry Kane v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen khi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGi\u1edd th\u00ec sao? Sau 4 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn kinh nghi\u1ec7m. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, l\u00e0 t\u00ednh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. L\u1ea5y v\u00ed d\u1ee5 Luke Amos ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i g\u1ea7n tr\u1ecdn c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tottenham-vs-ac-milan-07h30-ngay-18-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192426.html\">Tottenham 1-0 AC Milan (KT): Rossoneri b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn v\u00ec d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-phai-mua-kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang-172-192400.html\">Tottenham nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u01a1 b\u1eafp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-172-192372.html\">V\u00ec c\u00e2u n\u00f3i n\u00e0y, Pochettino khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Tottenham lo ngay ng\u00e1y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-khang-dinh-khong-mua-lai-gareth-bale-172-192272.html\">Pochettino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua l\u1ea1i Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1877","checkdouble":"192475"},{"date":"15:38 01/08","title":"3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/3-tru-cot-cat-giam-ky-nghi-tap-trung-som-cung-mu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones, Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n, song Mourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 3 tu\u1ea7n, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Doi-hinh-MU-don-tin-mung-tu-3-tru-cot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Marouane Fellaini, Romelu Lukaku, Phil Jones, Ashley Young, Jesse Lingard, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Paul Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng M.U, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111ang v\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Valencia, Smalling v\u00e0 Matic \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c nhau, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u01b0ng \u00fd, chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones, Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku\" title=\"Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-Romelu-Lukaku-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLukaku, Rashford v\u00e0 Jones \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Lindelof. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9\u00a0 Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Hi\u1ec7n Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire l\u00e0 2 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1876","checkdouble":"192478"}]}